-- Sri Lanka's Asian Hotels and Properties Quarterly Profit More Than Doubles
-- Anusha Ondaatjie
-- 2010-07-29T01:33:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/sri-lanka-s-asian-hotels-and-properties-quarterly-profit-more-than-doubles.html

          
          
             Asian Hotels and Properties Plc.,
a Colombo-based hotel and property management company, posted
profit of 188 million rupees ($1.7 million) in the first
quarter ended June 30, compared with 54 million rupees a year
earlier, according to a statement to the Colombo Stock
Exchange.  
